author: Cleo Abram
description:
Let’s play a game! All of these animals lived with the dinosaurs. And then…the asteroid hit. 

Here are three match-ups, can you guess which of the two animals survived?

If you got them all right, subscribe!

These visuals were from the American Museum of Natural History’s newest exhibit - go check it out!

#science #AMNH #asteroid #dinosaurs #shorts #animation
title: Guess Which Animal Survives
